Class OUAnimatedObject

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      ou.OUAnimatedObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public abstract class OUAnimatedObject
extends java.util.Observable
implements java.lang.Cloneable

OUAnimatedObject forms the base class of all objects used in M250 which have a graphical representation in a microworld.
